<td><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/ora"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">ora<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></td>
